:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"4 g","fat":"2 g","uom":"per 1 slice","carbohydrates":"1 g","calories":"140 kJ \/ 34 kcal"},"usefulItems":"heat-resistant cling film, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["<i>Serve this colourful chicken galantine with its zesty sauce as a starter with salad, at a picnic, at a buffet, or in a sandwich. Making your own cold cuts means you know exactly what you are feeding your family and friends, and you can also leave out or add ingredients to your liking.<\/i>","Chicken galantine can also be sliced very thinly and enjoyed in a sandwich, or on bread with some of the sauce."],"basicInfo":["medium","25m","3h 25m","40 slices"]}